{"tid":1044701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網友票選《海賊王》娜美人選 30歲泉里香突圍而出奪冠","createTime":"2019-03-03T05:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T06:53:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a72c8696455406e200f118a33672ae872418e1bc","tid":1044701,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"日前日本網友票選，誰最夠格稱為日本動漫《航海王》裡頭，擁有纖細蠻腰與波濤洶湧上圍的女航海士，心目中「真人版娜美」的女星，由於「娜美」是漫畫迷無可取代的虛擬女神之一，該次獲得冠軍是女星泉里香，不過她一直在演藝圈載浮載沉，反遭漫畫迷質疑憑什麼能得冠軍？此舉引發網友們熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/25/1798210-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F1798210-XXL.jpg&h=d8ddbeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泉里香被選為「真人版娜美」冠軍的不二人選。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/25/1798208-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F1798208-XXL.jpg&h=034711cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年30歲的女星泉里香，一直時裝雜誌御用模特兒，2003年曾演出真人版《美少女戰士》，該片捧紅飾演火星仙子的女星北川景子，讓她星路大開成為日本一線女星，反觀演出「水星仙子」的泉里香卻是一齣劇兩樣情，非但沒有紅，在演藝圈表現平平，戲後還遇上合作雜誌停刊、經紀合約續約狀況、演出暫停的問題，整整困擾了她10年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/02/1805719-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F1805719-XXL.jpg&h=b8d3e877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泉里香去年幫讀賣巨人棒球隊擔任開球。<br />\n<br />\n直到2017年痛定思痛的泉里香，決定拋開玉女形象包袱，28歲的她才推出個人首本寫真集《Rika!》大賣。而奪冠的關鍵就是，去年更拍攝indeed求職網廣告，就是扮演《航海王》的真人娜美，完勝於其它角色設定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/02/1805690-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F1805690-XXL.jpg&h=e276e0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泉里香曾演出《美少女戰士》中「水星仙子」（左二）從此演藝事業一蹶不振。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBUiEEb.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=918&amp;y=580\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBUiEEb.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D918%26y%3D580&h=f31ef07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲完半場前美斯攔截拉莫斯，後者避過後「抽水」，左手擊中對手嘴部，美斯痛極倒地。<br />\n<br />\n包括飾演魯夫的齋藤工被嫌老，扮演劍客索隆的池內博之被說過胖，更別提崩壞的香吉士（窪塚洋介飾演），泉里香完全視為毫無違和感，最佳「娜美」代言人，可以說是敗也動漫，成也動漫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/02/25/1798207-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F02%2F25%2F1798207-XXL.jpg&h=71d38ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泉里香在廣告中《航海王》扮演「真人版娜美」最為成功。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wdKhHfoGN7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwdKhHfoGN7k&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=4bde4231\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wdKhHfoGN7k</a><br />\n▲indeed求職網廣告。"},{"pid":"2a794a3d9e2319b08bc3a10f5317d7f1a4899b25","tid":1044701,"uid":239954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27defcc9a0c54208c6d4754e7a4b3dda2c59ecd5","tid":1044701,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:56:57.000Z","msg":"打得好!"},{"pid":"58454d31ca5204ae715814cb739ff3f3bc77c606","tid":1044701,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"日本娛圈唔走搞笑/戲劇路線 女人三十歲先黎紅 佢都可以話係奇跡"},{"pid":"5587c9f640b7dbc8ec809a8c268258edc81be52e","tid":1044701,"uid":102356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"無千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8284dee5be28a61a1573130662695ec0f69a1f17","tid":1044701,"uid":211656,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"個樣好殘"},{"pid":"6fc6b66660d84f5331540529fdf4c795118dbf90","tid":1044701,"uid":25560,"like":